  <brief_title>Purified CD34+ Cells Versus Peripheral Blood Mononuclear Cells in Treatment of Critical Limb Ischemia</brief_title>
  <official_title>Randomized Control Trial on Purified CD34+ Cells Versus Peripheral Blood Mononuclear Cells in Treatment of Critical Limb Ischemia</official_title>
